The application is packaged as a fat-Jar which is a Jar together with its dependency Jars into a single executable Jar file.
The Maven POM file contains all the appropriate information for it. 

Run the Maven goal
-------------------
Maven package

To Run the server
------------------
Open a command console and type:
java -jar target/RemoteReportServerRESTDropwizardJersey-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar server report.yml

Use the service to download a CSV file:
----------------------------------------
Open a web browsers and type the url:
http://localhost:8080/application/assets/
